Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.05,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我能與　做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.05,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(625,12)}你
